# .ragignore
#
# Same syntax as .gitignore. Use this to keep rag-utils from indexing
# files that are technically tracked by git but aren't useful as
# "code context" for an AI assistant (generated files, fixtures, etc).
#
# .gitignore is always respected automatically - you only need to
# list EXTRA exclusions here.

# Example exclusions:
# *.generated.ts
# **/__fixtures__/**
# **/*.snap
# docs/
